title: ERA MSS overall system status
agents: snmp
author: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH <info@kuhn-ruess.de>
license: GPL
distribution: none
description:
 Reads the rollup status cells from the ERA MSS main branch (OID .1.3.6.1.4.1.11588.1.5.100).
 One service per target processor (tpAsterixStatus, tpServerStatus, rxs, inputData)
 plus an aggregated "System" service that bundles txs, rmtr, rack and networkDevices.
 Each status value is mapped to Checkmk state via the common ERA status map
 (OKA/ON/ACTIVE/BACKUP → OK, WAR/DEG → WARN, ERR/OFF/NOC → CRIT, UNK/n/a → UNKNOWN).

item:
 "TP <index>" for per-target-processor entries, "System" for the global rollup.

inventory:
 One service per populated tpTable row plus one "System" service if any of the
 global rollup cells are present.
